Vitty Has to Leave
Verse 1:
Let's write this song, the mother of it!
So that they never play it on the radio.
So that they never called it pop,
And its sound doesn't suck
 
Chorus:
Stop it! Stop it! Vitty, Vitty has to leave.
Stop it! Stop it! Vitty, Vitty has to leave.
Stop it! Stop it! Vitty, Vitty has to leave.
Stop it! Stop it! Vitty, Vitty has to leave.
 
To Turkey or to Egypt, Vitty has to leave.
To sauna or to pee — Vitty has to leave.
Vitty on repeat. Vitty has to leave.
 
Vitty has to...
Vitty has to leave!
Vitty has to...
Vitty has to leave!
 
Verse 2:
Stop this music, —
It does not give people rest.
Stop this beat, —
Vitty dances, Vitty doesn't sleep.
 
Chorus:
Stop it! Stop it! Vitty, Vitty has to leave.
Stop it! Stop it! Vitty, Vitty has to leave.
Stop it! Stop it! Vitty, Vitty has to leave.
Stop it! Stop it! Vitty, Vitty has to leave.
 
To Turkey or to Egypt, Vitty has to leave.
To sauna or to pee — Vitty has to leave.
Vitty on repeat. Vitty has to leave.
 
Vitty has to...
Vitty has to leave!
Vitty has to...
Vitty has to leave!
